===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States Census|2020 census]], the population was 918. The racial makeup of the town was 87.69% [[white (U.S. Census)|White]], 2.07% [[African American (U.S. Census)|Black or African American]], 0.00% [[Native American (U.S. Census)|Native American]], 1.42% [[Asian (U.S. Census)|Asian]], 0.00% [[Pacific Islander (U.S. Census)|Pacific Islander]], 2.40% from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 6.43% from two or more races. [[Hispanic (U.S. Census)|Hispanic]] or [[Latino (U.S. Census)|Latino]] of any race were 6.43% of the population.<ref name="Census 2020" />

